The paper deals with linear precoding techniques for multiuser, multi-antenna transmitters, which is a topic that falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses power allocation and user selection, which are topics that fall under the signal processing (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT and cs.NI, followed by cs.SI, cs.MM, and cs.LG.
